This software requires Numpy ( http://numpy.scipy.org )
    and PyOpenGL ( http://pyopengl.sf.net )

To run this software, use:
    python main.py
which will output usage information to the console.

An example linkage -- the Peaucellier-Lipkin linkage -- is
provided. To load it, use:
    python main.py peaucellier.txt

For more information, see:
    http://mit.edu/harold/Public/linkage
